Location CRG offers a heavy equipment rental service, including the rental of mini-excavators and mini-excavators on the South Shore of Montreal. We have a wide variety of equipment in excellent condition for your work. In addition, our operators are all professionals with many years of experience.

If you are an entrepreneur who needs an excavator, loader, compactor, tractor or mini loader, do not hesitate to contact us. We are the team for you.
